<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//APACHE//DTD Documentation V2.0//EN" "http://forrest.apache.org/dtd/document-v20.dtd">
<document xml:lang="fi">
    <header>
        <title>Installing, configuring and switching keyboards in
        Windows 10</title>
    </header>
    <body>
      <section>
      <title>Installation</title>
        <ol>
          <li>Go to the <a
            href="http://divvun.no/no/keyboards/desktopindex.html">Divvun
            keyboard download page</a>, and click on the
            <strong>download link for Windows 10</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/01_download-sme-en.png"
            alt="Download"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Run</strong> the downloaded installer:
            <p><img src="images/win10/02_run-installer-sme-en.png"
            alt="Run installer"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Allow</strong> the installer to make changes:
            <p><img src="images/win10/03_allow_changes-sme-en.png"
            alt="Allow changes"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Select installer language:
            <p><img src="images/win10/04_select_inst_lang-sme-en.png"
            alt="Select installer language"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Choose install location, the default is fine:
            <p><img src="images/win10/05_inst_location-sme-en.png"
            alt="Installation location"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Select Start Menu location, the default is fine:
            <p><img src="images/win10/06_start_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Start menu"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>You are now ready to install:
            <p><img src="images/win10/07_ready_to_install-sme-en.png"
            alt="Ready to install"/></p>
            <p><img src="images/win10/08_installing-sme-en.png"
            alt="Installing"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>You have to <strong>Restart</strong> after installation to ensure
            the keyboard is working properly:
            <p><img src="images/win10/09_restart-sme-en.png" alt="Restart"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>After the restart, the new keyboard(s) should show up in the
            keyboard menu (if not, continue as described below):
            <p><img src="images/win10/10_keyboard_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Keyboard menu"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
      <title>Configuration</title>
        <p>The installation done above should automatically have turned on the
        installed keyboards. In case it has not happened, or you want to change
        the configuration, do as follows:</p>
  
        <ol>
            <li>Mene <strong>Aloitus</strong>-valikkoon, ja klikkaa
                <strong>Asetukset</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/start_menu-fi.png" alt="Startmeny"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Mene <strong>Aika ja kieli</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-fi.png" alt="Kontrollpanel"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Paina <strong>Lisää kieli</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-time_and_lang-fi.png" alt="Språk" /></p>
            </li>
            <li>Valitse <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> klikkaamalla sitä:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-fi.png" alt="Legg til språk"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Valitse seuraavista <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> joka sopii sinulle:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-finland-fi.png" alt="Regionale varianter"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Merkkaa <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> ja paina <strong>Asetukset</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-modify-sme-fi.png" alt="Språk etter å ha valgt nordsamisk"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Paina <strong>Lisää näppäimistö</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-keyboard-fi.png" alt="Språkalternativer"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Valitse <strong>Saame, Suomen ja Ruotsin kieliversiot</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-finland-sweden-fi.png" alt="Inndatametode"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Merkkaa <strong>Suomi ja saame</strong> ja paina <strong>Poista</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-remove-finnish_with_sami-keyboard-fi.png"
                alt="Språkalternativer: Fjern norsk med samisk"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Silloin on <strong>Davvisámegiella (Suopma)</strong> kuin
                sisäänkieli näppäimistöllä <strong>Saame, Suomen ja Ruotsin kieliversiot</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/keyboard-done-sme-fi.png"
                alt="Språk med nordsamisk ferdigvalgt"/></p>
            </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
      <title>Switching keyboards</title>
        <ol>
            <li>Vaihtaminen kielten välillä tapahtuu
                <strong>Windows+väli</strong> kunnes pohjoissaame näppäimistö on aktiivinen:
                <p><img src="images/win10/switching-keyboards-sme-fi.png"
                alt="Språk med nordsamisk ferdigvalgt"/></p>
            </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
    </body>
</document>
